We usually take a look at
specific applications and how

00:00:19.470 --> 00:00:23.680
their user interfaces can be
improved using the elements of

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:26.125
Android design, which are very
well documented on the Android

00:00:26.125 --> 00:00:27.340
Design site.

00:00:27.340 --> 00:00:31.930
But today, we're going to be
looking at rich notifications

00:00:31.930 --> 00:00:35.960
and local video players, as you
can see here in our slide.

00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:37.000
Before we get started,
we should

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.220
probably introduce ourselves.

00:00:39.220 --> 00:00:42.050
As always, my name
is Roman Nurik.

00:00:42.050 --> 00:00:42.920
ADAM KOCH: Hi, guys.

