ROMAN NURIK: So, I mean, adding
something to the queue

00:08:07.445 --> 00:08:08.200
is a good question.

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:11.460
We haven't really-- again, we
haven't gone into video

00:08:11.460 --> 00:08:14.300
playback or video
detail screens.

00:08:14.300 --> 00:08:16.210
But I envisage that it will--
is that even a word?

00:08:16.210 --> 00:08:16.750
Envisage?

00:08:16.750 --> 00:08:21.010
Yeah, I'd imagine that when you
long press any video from

00:08:21.010 --> 00:08:24.000
anywhere, you enter
a contextual--

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:26.295
I guess the contextual selection
mode, and they you

00:08:26.295 --> 00:08:27.860
can long press multiple
videos.

00:08:27.860 --> 00:08:30.270
And then in the contextual
action bar, you can have kind

00:08:30.270 --> 00:08:32.600
of In Queue or Add to Queue.

