00:28:07.850 --> 00:28:11.360
difficult-to-discover feature,
and it's not necessarily

00:28:11.360 --> 00:28:14.460
well-labeled, like some sort
of gesture or something.

00:28:14.460 --> 00:28:17.730
Showcase View is a little tool
that'll give you this kind of

00:28:17.730 --> 00:28:25.360
